title: Wet Pizza Compilation: Vol. 1
description:
This is a comp album featuring some of the biggest names in American power noise. For anyone interested in power noise, who can't seem to find anything worth a shit to listen to, this is a perfect starter album. The music on this album is unlike anything else out there, and will make a fantastic addition to any respectable music collection.

Says Denvertronic.com about the album:

"The much trumpeted Wet Pizza Compilation is finally here! There are many artists on this compilation, with a few of them residing in Denver. The styles range from noise, gabber, industrial, all the way up to grindcore. Highly recommended experimental album..."

This torrent is mp3 format, 128kbps.
